Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataModel.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeName, Item, ItemAttribute, Seller

    public abstract class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the superclass of many others. It contains information about the state of the object in relation to the database as well as utility methods for accessing the database.
